caller_intent: Randy Howard from Mutual Reports needs to contact policyholder Axel Bernal Poland to reschedule a homeowner's insurance inspection after the initial phone number provided was invalid.
resolution_steps: Agent asked Randy for the policy number to look up contact information.
Agent checked their system and found an alternative phone number (336-782-0476) associated with the policyholder.
Agent confirmed this was the only other number on file and suggested Randy try it.
knowledge_required: Access to policyholder contact information via policy number lookup
Understanding of insurance inspection follow-up procedures
summary: Randy Howard from Mutual Reports contacted Alliance Insurance to resolve an issue with an invalid policyholder phone number for a scheduled inspection. The agent looked up the policy using the provided number (572-798-2) and found an alternative contact number (336-782-0476) for Axel Bernal Poland. The call concluded with the agent providing this number for Randy to attempt contacting the policyholder.
